{{vgname|巫术VI：禁断之魔笔|en=Wizardry VI: Bane of the Cosmic Forge}}是一款由[[Sir-Tech|Sir-Tech]]制作和发行的[[电子角色扮演游戏|电子角色扮演游戏]]。本游戏为[[巫术系列|巫术系列]]的第6作，游戏最初于1990年发行。<ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamefaqs.com/pc/564807-wizardry-vi-bane-of-the-cosmic-forge/data| title = Release information| publisher = [[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]| date = | accessdate = 2017-01-16| archive-date = 2015-10-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151015020717/http://www.gamefaqs.com/pc/564807-wizardry-vi-bane-of-the-cosmic-forge/data| dead-url = no}}</ref>

David Bradley完全重写了本游戏的系统。

《[[電腦遊戲世界|電腦遊戲世界]]》赞扬了本游戏的武器技能、用户界面、图像等。<ref name="clupper199102">{{cite news | url=http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1991&pub=2&id=79 | title=Wizardry Forges into the 21st Century / Sir-Tech's Bane of the Cosmic Forge | work=Computer Gaming World | date=February 1991 | accessdate=17 November 2013 | author=Clupper, Marc | pages=30 | archive-date=2021-02-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217181125/http://www.cgwmuseum.org/galleries/index.php?year=1991&pub=2&id=79 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

